item.title: Divide and Conquer by the Elites FREE YOUR MIND| WHEN WILL WE COME TOGETHER?
item.description: “I knew I couldn’t kill them. More powerful men than me have tried. But if I could get them to kill eachother…” - Zemo. SEE THROUGH THE ILLUSION AND THE AGENDA THAT IS BEING WAGED ON US. All of these hate crimes on the news and mainstream is to DIVIDE AND CONQUER US. They dont want us coming TOGETHER as a community and putting our differences to the side! If that were to happen, we’ll be too powerful than these higher ups and puppet on a string!
